html." ([2018]):[2] "Product Information. Vyndaqel (tafamidis)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.[3] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[4] "Product Information. Hivid (zalcitabine)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.', 1767363022);
